1. npm install will create npm_modules directory and fetch the modules. run npm_modules (if not already run)
2. copy numbro to npm_modules
    the folder should contain
     'numbro.js'
     'languages.js'
     and the folder 'languages'

the following files have been changed so as to replace numeral.js with numbro.js
package.json
src/core.js
src/editor/numericEditor.js
src/editor/numericRendered.js
grunt build will create the handsontable.js in dist folder
